<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="lack-v">lack <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /læk/    美 /læk/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[不用于被动语态] 缺乏；短少；没有：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>At first I lacked confidence.
起初，我缺乏自信。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They lacked the money to send him to university.
他们没钱送他上大学。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="lack-for-nothing">lack (for) nothing</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[正式用语] 什么也不缺：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>As he is very rich he lacks for nothing. 
他很富有，什么都不缺。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>lacking /'lækɪŋ/ adj   </p>
<h3 id="be-lacking-in-sth">be lacking in sth</h3>
<p>1.<strong>缺少某物</strong>  </p></div>